::Orchestra::

       Orchestra smacked himself on the head.

        *Damn!* he thought, *I didn't even tell 'er my name!  This isn't my
code of honour!*

        "I'm very sorry for not introducing myself, I do appologize.  My
name differs from place to place.  Some know me as "The band", some know me
as "The artist" but please, I highly prefer the name Orchestra!" He said in
his usually cheery voice.
